history.content: If you are worrying about "if I need to take 188 before 189?" the answer is not. 188 is pretty easy and 189 needs very little from 188.
Has anyone taken 188 and 189 in the same semester? What are your thoughts?
history.subject: CS 188 and 189 Together

history.content:

On a separate note, has anyone taken 188 and 189 in the same semester? What are your thoughts?
